Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是救了我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛龍在龍宮島航線上展開了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話 5分鐘後將到達第二防衛圈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要老師 能改變航向嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要花上半天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不破壞內核就沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我就去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我扔過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認本島被擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 總比島被破壞要好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偽裝鏡面解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力波防護罩展開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳 傳來了…歌聲…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這歌聲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰在唱歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道該怎麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,質問者型 已消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子是完全醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個島是…這地方原來有島嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:17:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地圖上沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,17區偵察機 Youngstar-2呼叫新聯合國總部
